hy pRBU! (inqwxy ho jwx dy kwrn jIvW dy AMdroN) sihm dI gMF nhIN KulHdI[
(ikauNik) kwm, kRoD, mwieAw (dw moh), AhMkwr qy eIrKw-swVw-iehnW pMjW ny rl ky (sB jIvW dy Awqmk guxW nUM) lu`t ilAw hY ]1] rhwau]
(kwmwidk dI lu`t dy kwrn, jIvW dy AMdroN ieh hMkwr nhIN jWdw) ik AsIN bVy kvI hW, cMgI kul vwly hW, ivdvwn hW, jogI hW, sMinAwsI hW,
igAwnvwn hW, guxvwn hW, sUrmy hW jW dwqy hW; iksy vyly BI ieh (bxI hoeI) smJ nhIN htdI ik (ijhVy BI pwsy pey ausy dw hI mwx ho igAw) ]2]
hy rivdws! (ijn@W nUM kwmwidkW ny lu`t ilAw hY, auh) swry hI kmilAW vWg ZlqI Kw rhy hn qy (ieh) nhIN smJdy (ik izMdgI dw Asl Awsrw pRBU dw nwm hY);
mYnUM rivdws nUM prmwqmw dw nwm hI Awsrw hY, nwm hI myrI ijMd hY, nwm hI myry pRwx hn, nwm hI myrw Dn hY ]3]1]
rwg rwmklI iv`c Bgq byxI jI dI bwxI[
Akwl purK ie`k hY Aqy siqgurU dI ikrpw nwl imldw hY[
(jo mnu`K gurU dI ikrpw nwl aus myl-AvsQw ivc A`piVAw hY, aus dy vwsqy) ieVw, ipMgulw qy suKmnw iqMny hI ie`ko QW v`sdIAW hn,
iqRbyxI sMgm pRRXwg qIrQ BI (aus mnu`K leI) au~Qy v`sdw hY[ Bwv, aus mnu`K nUM ieVw ipMglw suKmnw dy AiBAws dI loV nhIN rih jWdI; aus nUM iqRbyxI qy pRXwg dy ieSnwn dI loV nhIN rihMdI[ (aus mnu`K dw) mn pRBU dy (imlwp-rUp iqRbyxI ivc) ieSnwn krdw hY ]1]
hy sMq jno! mwieAw-rihq rwm aus AvsQw ivc (mnu`K dy mn ivc) v`sdw hY,
ijs AvsQw nwl sWJ koeI ivrlw mnu`K siqgurU dI srn pY ky bxWdw hY[
au~Qy (aus Av`sQw iv`c) inrMjn sohxw rwm prgt huMdw hY ]1] rhwau]
(jy koeI pu`Cy ik) ijs AvsQw ivc pRBU (mn dy AMdr) Aw itkdw hY, aus dIAW inSwnIAW kIh hn (qW au~qr ieh hY ik)
aus AvsQw ivc siqgurU dw Sbd pRBU dI is&q-swlwh dI bwxI (mnu`K dy ihrdy ivc) hulwrw pYdw krdy hn;
(jgq dy hnyry nUM dUr krn leI) cMd qy sUrj (auqny smr`Q) nhIN (ijqnw auh hulwrw mn dy hnyry nUM dUr krn leI huMdw hY), paux pwxI (Awidk q`q jgq nUM auqnw suK) nhIN (dy skdy, ijqnw suK ieh hulwrw mnu`K dy mn nUM dyNdw hY);
mnu`K dI surq gurU dI is`iKAw nwl jwg pYNdI hY, gurU dI rwhIN sUJ pY jWdI hY ]2]
(pRBU-imlwp vwlI AvsQw ivc mnu`K dI) pRBU nwl fUMGI jwx-pCwx ho jWdI hY[ mMdI m`q nws ho jWdI hY;
au~cI aufwrI ivc (A`piVAw hoieAw mn) nwm-AMimRq dy rs nwl rs jWdw hY;
jo mnu`K ies (AvsQw ivc A`pV skx vwly) hunr dw Byd jwx lYNdw hY,
aus nUM Akwl purK iml pYNdw hY ]3]
AphuMc, byAMq qy prm purK pRBU dy prgt hox dw itkwxw (mnu`Kw srIr dw idmwZ-rUp) dsvW bUhw hY;
srIr dy auqly ih`sy ivc (isr, mwno) iek h`t hY, aus h`t ivc (idmwZ, mwno) iek Awlw hY, ies Awly dI rwhIN pRBU dw pRkwS huMdw hY ]4]
(ijs dy AMdr prmwqmw prgt ho ipAw) auh sdw jwgdw rihMdw hY (sucyq rihMdw hY), (mwieAw dI nINd ivc) kdy sauNdw nhIN;
auh iek AYsI smwDI ivc itikAw rihMdw hY ijQoN mwieAw dy iqMny gux qy iqMnW lokW dI mwieAw pry hI rihMdy hn;
auh mnu`K pRBU dw nwm mMqR Awpxy ihrdy ivc itkw r`Kdw hY,
(ijs dI brkiq nwl) aus dw mn mwieAw vloN prq ky (sucyq rihMdw hY), aus AvsQw ivc itkwxw pkVdw hY ijQy koeI Purnw nhIN auTdw ]5]
auh mnu`K sdw jwgdw hY, (sucyq rihMdw hY), kdy JUT nhIN boldw;
pMjW hI ieMidRAW nUM Awpxy kwbU ivc r`Kdw hY,
siqgurU dw aupdyS Awpxy mn ivc sWB ky r`Kdw hY,
Awpxw mn, Awpxw srIr pRBU dy ipAwr qoN sdky krdw hY ]6]
auh mnu`K (jgq nUM) h`Q (dIAW au~glW, ru`K dIAW) tihxIAW qy p`qr smJdw hY[
(ies vwsqy mUl pRBU nUM C`f ky ies iKlwry ivc ru`J ky) AwpxI izMdgI jUey dI Kyf ivc nhIN gvwauNdw;
ivkwrW dI nINd dw somw hI bMd kr dyNdw hY,
mn nUM AigAwnqw dy hnyry vloN prqw ky (ies ivc igAwn dw) sUrj cVHwauNdw hY;
(aus dy AMdr imlwp dw) iek cSmw Pu`t pYNdw hY[ (auh iek AYsI mOj) mwxdw hY, ijs nUM kdy buFypw nhIN (Bwv, jo kdy mu`kdI nhIN)[
(auh sdw leI) prmwqmw nwl myl kr lYNdw hY ]7]
pRBU dI joiq duAwrw aus dy AMdr (mwno) cwr mUMhW vwlw dIvw jg pYNdw hY (ijs krky hr pwsy cwnx hI cwnx rihMdw hY);
(aus dy AMdr, mwno, iek AYsw Pu`l iKV pYNdw hY, ijs dy) ivckwr pRBU-rUp mkrMd huMdw hY qy aus dIAW byAMq p`qIAW huMdIAW hn[
(AnMq rcnw vwlw pRBU aus dy AMdr prgt ho pYNdw hY) auh mnu`K swrIAW qwkqW dy mwlk pRBU nUM Awpxy AMdr vsw lYNdw hY[
aus dw mn moqI (bx ky pRBU dy gux rUp) rqnW ivc juiVAw rihMdw hY ]8]
(aus dI brkiq nwl) aus dy m`Qy au~qy (mwno) kaul Pu`l (iKV pYNdw hY, qy) aus Pu`l dy cwr cuPyry hIry (proqy jWdy hn);
aus bMdy dy Dur AMdr iqRlokI dw mwlk pRBU Aw itkdw hY[
(aus dy AMdr mwno iek AYsw suMdr rwg huMdw hY ik (pMjy hI iksmW dy sohxy swj v`j pYNdy hn,
bVy sMK v`jx l`g pYNdy hn, aus auqy cOr Ju`l pYNdw hY (Bwv, aus dw mn SwhnSwhW dw Swh bx jWdw hY)[
siqgurU qoN imilAw hoieAw pRBU dy nwm dw ieh cwnx kwmwidk ivkwrW nUM mwr mukWdw hY[
hy pRBU! (qyrw dws) byxI (BI qyry dr qoN) (ieh) nwm hI mMgdw hY ]9]1]
